Text:
I've seen this movie several times over the years, and I'm not quite sure what all these scenes are supposed to add up to.  As porno films go, it seems to have ambitions toward some kind of character study, and the star, Jessie St. James, actually seems to have some genuine acting ability. She's tall, athletic blonde, gorgeous, and she brings a real intensity to her sex scenes... and she likes to swallow cum!

It's as close to a real classic as any porn film can be.  With Desiree Costeau (who can't act...   but who cares?) and Georgina Spelvin.
